code: @Override public Response newResponse() {     return new Response(). }
@Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     info = in.readMap(). }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeMap(info). }
@Override public XContentBuilder toXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     builder.map(info).     return builder. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj == null) {         return false.     }     if (getClass() != obj.getClass()) {         return false.     }     Response other = (Response) obj.     return Objects.equals(info, other.info). }
